For original README, please visit source repository from which it was forked:
https://github.com/the3dfxdude/7kaa


Introduction
------------

Intention of this fork is to change some (or many?) initial values of original
game and to make some things harder (but not necessarily more balanced).
This readme should be kept in sync with new changes as they are commited.


New things/settings/limits introduced in this repository
--------------------------------------------------------
* Increased monster variety on maps from 3 to 8
* Units attack takes armor into consideration when computing damage points
	for more information, please refer to this thread:
		https://www.7kfans.com/forums/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=755
	and this wiki page:
		https://www.7kfans.com/wiki/index.php/Unit_and_attack_information
* Game is not paused when window loses focus